REQUIREMENTS BEFORE MAGSIMULA
  - XAMPP (kailangan naka-ON yung Apache at MySQL)
  - PHPMyAdmin access: http://localhost/phpmyadmin

 I-SETUP MUNA YUNG DATABASE

- sa phpmyadmin

- Gumawa ng bagong database:
     - Database name: rentramuros_database
     - Click "Create"

- I-import yung base database (ito munabago yung isa):
     - Click "Import" tab sa itaas
     - I-upload yung: database/rentramuros_database.sql
     - Click "Import"

- I-import yung queuing system schema (ITO YUNG PANGALAWA):
     - Click "Import" ulit 
     - I-upload yung: database/queuing_system.sql
     - Click "Go" / "Import"
     - or run mo na lang yung sql pwede rin

